Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.10,0:00:06.36,mondaiji zhengwen,,0,0,0,,无聊 真无聊啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.76,0:00:08.38,mondaiji zhengwen,,0,0,0,,大小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.80,0:00:12.26,mondaiji zhengwen,,0,0,0,,我知道啦 只要说服老爷子就行了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.80,0:00:16.92,mondaiji zhengwen,,0,0,0,,让他同意GHQ施行的财阀解体政策
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.44,0:00:20.74,mondaiji zhengwen,,0,0,0,,要不要一些凉饮料
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.40,0:00:21.80,mondaiji zhengwen,,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.70,0:00:34.90,mondaiji zhengwen,,0,0,0,,谁都不会违抗我命令的世界 真是无聊又没用
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.72,0:00:38.12,mondaiji zhengwen,,0,0,0,,但是这样才有离开的价值
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.60,0:00:40.82,mondaiji zhengwen,,0,0,0,,抛弃这个家的全部
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.66,0:00:49.54,mondaiji zhengwen,,0,0,0,,飞鸟 飞鸟 你醒了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.76,0:00:52.44,mondaiji zhengwen,,0,0,0,,嗯 醒了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.32,0:00:59.58,mondaiji zhengwen,,0,0,0,,早上好 春日部 还有莉莉
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.36,0:01:01.54,mondaiji zhengwen,,0,0,0,,早安
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.98,0:01:03.26,mondaiji zhengwen,,0,0,0,,飞鸟 这个
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.96,0:01:21.02,mondaiji zhengwen,,0,0,0,,明明没必要陪着我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.70,0:01:25.04,mondaiji zhengwen,,0,0,0,,不过他也算在努力做好一个头领啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.26,0:01:30.06,mondaiji zhengwen,,0,0,0,,十六夜君！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.52,0:01:33.08,mondaiji zhengwen,,0,0,0,,啊 大小姐 晚安
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.96,0:01:37.00,mondaiji zhengwen,,0,0,0,,给我起来
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.38,0:01:46.04,mondaiji zhengwen,,0,0,0,,哇 仁君
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.66,0:01:52.24,mondaiji zhengwen,,0,0,0,,喂喂 大小姐啊 一上来就这么玩会死人的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.30,0:01:54.66,mondaiji zhengwen,,0,0,0,,紧急状况 你看这个
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.22,0:02:12.06,mondaiji zhengwen,,0,0,0,,火龙诞生祭？北边的美术工艺品展示会和评价会 由各种各样的人举办的恩惠游戏 主要比赛是由阶层支配者举办的大会
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.26,0:02:17.74,mondaiji zhengwen,,0,0,0,,魂淡 这不是很有趣么 不去玩玩么
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.30,0:02:19.34,mondaiji zhengwen,,0,0,0,,兴致真高啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.32,0:02:21.42,mondaiji zhengwen,,0,0,0,,这是怎么弄到的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.38,0:02:24.56,mondaiji zhengwen,,0,0,0,,黑兔好像故意把这个藏起来了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.14,0:02:27.38,mondaiji zhengwen,,0,0,0,,春日部碰巧发现了这个
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.84,0:02:28.88,mondaiji zhengwen,,0,0,0,,碰巧而已
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.46,0:02:31.72,mondaiji zhengwen,,0,0,0,,是么 保密啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.70,0:02:39.50,mondaiji zhengwen,,0,0,0,,不 不能去啊 你觉得从这里到北面的境界壁要多久啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.98,0:02:45.14,mondaiji zhengwen,,0,0,0,,居然对我们隐藏这么有趣的祭典 哭
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.72,0:02:50.34,mondaiji zhengwen,,0,0,0,,一直为了共同体努力过来了 真是杯具 哭
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.86,0:02:56.88,mondaiji zhengwen,,0,0,0,,看来我们有必要让黑兔他们尝点苦头了 哭
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.60,0:02:57.86,mondaiji zhengwen,,0,0,0,,嘿
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.74,0:03:00.66,mondaiji zhengwen,,0,0,0,,那个……你们有在听么
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.40,0:03:10.82,mondaiji zhengwen,,0,0,0,,至黑兔 我们要去参加北面和东面境界壁的火龙诞生祭了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.50,0:03:14.28,mondaiji zhengwen,,0,0,0,,作为隐瞒祭典的惩罚
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.66,0:03:20.20,mondaiji zhengwen,,0,0,0,,今天如果抓不住我们的话 我们就退出组织
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.52,0:03:21.62,mondaiji zhengwen,,0,0,0,,拼命来找我们吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.94,0:03:29.24,mondaiji zhengwen,,0,0,0,,这群问题儿童们！
Comment: 0,0:03:30.28,0:03:30.58,mondaiji zhengwen,,0,0,0,,OP
